translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 準備はきっちりしていかんとな
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We have to make sure we're properly prepared.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「たぶん、今回はそこまでいかないと思うけどね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I don't think it'll get that intense this time, though.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そういえば……翔竜山は前人未踏。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Come to think of it... Mount Shoryu is unclimbed by anyone before.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 高さも測定不明だったはずだが……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Its height was supposed to be unknown as well...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 12000という数字はどこから来た？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Where did the figure '12,000' come from?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ああ、登ったんだ。ちょいと前にな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah, someone climbed it. Not too long ago.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ほう……流石は余のカオスマスター。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Oh... As expected from my Chaos Master.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そんな事までしていたか
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You even went that far?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あの時のことはあんまり思い出したくねーなー……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I really don't want to remember that time much...
Well, I'm still going to climb it.
Alright, let's climb with full force.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あの衛星野郎に目に物見せてくれるわ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'll show that satellite bastard a thing or two.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「はーーっ！　いーぃ景色ぃーー！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Haaah! What a beautiful view!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 山道を、ナギが先頭でどんどん進んでいく。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Nagi took the lead and swiftly proceeded along the mountain path.
Amazing!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: カラーの森が、あんなにちっちゃい！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The Kara forest looks so tiny from here!
Look, look, big sister!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あんまりはしゃぐと、後でバテるでー。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If you get too excited, you'll burn out later.
Take it easy.
I'm totally fine.
Boom baaah!
Ah, Nagi!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 元気に駆け出したナギを追って、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Chasing after Nagi who took off energetically,
Shizuka started running too.
Ah... are you okay...?
Haa, huu... I'm so tired...
My legs hurt...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ナギは早々に体力がなくなり、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Nagi quickly ran out of stamina,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 先頭グループから脱落していた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and fell behind from the lead group.
Geez...
What the hell are you doing?
Ugh, I got caught up with!
If you stop, I'll catch up.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: も少し歩け。先行ってる連中がキャンプ張ってる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Walk a bit more. The others ahead have set up camp.
Y-Yeah...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 頷くが、ナギの足取りは重い。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She nodded, but Nagi's steps were heavy.
Ugh, I guess it can't be helped...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ふむ、とアルカネーゼは眉を動かした。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmm, Arcanese raised an eyebrow.
Nagi, hold this umbrella.
Huh?
Hmm, hoist up!
Wah, whoaah!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: アルカネーゼはナギに傘を持たせて、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Arcanese handed Nagi the umbrella,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そのナギを肩車で持ち上げた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: then lifted Nagi onto her shoulders.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あっはっは、軽いなー、ナギは」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ahahaha, Nagi is so light.
Ah, w-wait... Is this okay?
Until the next campsite, that is.
